file_content.text: It's happening. It's all happening, and you can't stop it....
And with that, the Sith Academy is secure. I suppose saying "good work" would constitute a gross understatement.
Tell me what you know!
Start talking!
I propose a trade: you tell me everything, and I call for medical assistance.
Let's make a deal.
And you can't stop this.
Die already. [Kill him]
This Jedi commander--he said some odd things....
I'm sure Darth Arkous would like to hear about it. He's eager to offer up his congratulations in person.
It's too late for me. But I leave this place knowing I've set a great thing in motion....
No point threatening a dead man, Sith....
You should know by now you can't threaten a dead man, bounty hunter....
No point threatening a dead man, Imperial puppet....
You've really come through for the Empire. There is much for us to thank you for, and much yet to discuss; I hope we see you soon.
Press the attack!
The Sith Academy--disgusting!
The Empire won't even know what hit it!
I'm not only a Jedi--I'm a soldier!
I fight for something greater than myself!
This fight was inevitable!
I know more than a few tricks!
Enough sparring!
Did you really think you could take me?
You don't even have a clue, do you?
It's too late--we got what we came for!
Thought this would be a memorable fight!
You can't win!
Hardly impressive!
You can't... stop it....
